					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="trending-item">
					<img src="https://topscorer.qodeinteractive.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/h3-blog-img-5.jpg" alt="Full Customization" loading="lazy" />
					<div class="trending-overlay">
						<div class="trending-number">02</div>
						<div class="trending-meta">Customization</div>
						<h4 class="trending-title">Full Customization</h4>
						<p>Team colors, vinyl logos, and branding can be done.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<a href="/shop" class="trending-item trending-item-link">
					<img src="https://topscorer.qodeinteractive.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/h3-blog-img-4.jpg" alt="Quick Ship lockers" loading="lazy" />
					<div class="trending-overlay">
						<div class="trending-number">03</div>
						<div class="trending-meta">2–4 weeks</div>
						<h4 class="trending-title">Quick Ship</h4>
						<p>Some lockers and sizes are premade and ship quickly—no custom sizing or colors.</p>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/contact#quote-form" class="trending-item trending-item-link">
					<img src="https://topscorer.qodeinteractive.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/h3-blog-img-7.jpg" alt="Custom lockers" loading="lazy" />
					<div class="trending-overlay">
						<div class="trending-number">04</div>
						<div class="trending-meta">8–12 weeks</div>
						<h4 class="trending-title">Custom</h4>
						<p>Any size, any wood, phenolic, or other materials. We build it your way at a price that beats the rest.</p>
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Why Our Prices Section -->
	<section class="ranking-section" style="background: #f8f8f8;">
		<div class="ranking-container">
			<div class="ranking-image">
				<img src="https://topscorer.qodeinteractive.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/h3-img-1.jpg" alt="Custom Wood Sports Lockers" />
