					<div class="equipment-item-image">
						<img src="/images/topscorer/h3-blog-img-4.jpg" alt="Locker delivery and installation" loading="lazy" />
						<span class="equipment-circle">4</span>
					</div>
					<h4>Delivery & Installation</h4>
					<p>We deliver and install your lockers so your locker room is ready for your team.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="equipment-accordion">
