					<div class="accordion-header">
						<span>Free Custom Design Consultation</span>
						<span>+</span>
					</div>
					<div class="accordion-content">
						<p>Every project starts with a free custom design consultation. We'll discuss your needs, space, budget, and vision to understand exactly what you're looking for. No obligation, just expert advice from 30+ years of experience.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="accordion-item">
					<div class="accordion-header">
						<span>5 Year Warranty</span>
						<span>+</span>
					</div>
					<div class="accordion-content">
						<p>We're confident in the quality of our wood sports lockers and back every locker with a 5 year warranty. Our modular design means damaged parts can be replaced individually—no need to replace the entire locker.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="accordion-item">
					<div class="accordion-header">
						<span>Made to Your Liking</span>
						<span>+</span>
					</div>
					<div class="accordion-content">
						<p>We build lockers to your specs, your style, and your space. Choose from our Essential or Premium lines, quick ship or full custom—colors, sizes, and options are up to you. Tell us what you want and we'll make it happen.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="accordion-item">
					<div class="accordion-header">
						<span>Sport-Specific Solutions</span>
						<span>+</span>
					</div>
					<div class="accordion-content">
						<p>We have all the shapes and sizes that are required for most locker rooms. It is up to you and your style to choose from.</p>
